{
  "stem": "17626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 133.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother had diphtheria, and then I got that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she, she came out of the hospital and with diphtheria, you really have to watch your diet, I think.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her cousin was making fresh chicken livers with onions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And although the cousin didn't want to give it to her is the story that I got, Mom had very good persuasive powers-- and she had some.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that night, they had to call the doctor because-- and the doctor said, either she's going to die or she's going to make it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, there's nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thankfully, Mom had a good constitution and she made it through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] later on, when the Russians came, everybody left, everybody was evacuated out of there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The scarlet fever was later on, when we left Siberia en route to [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's from-- from this [RUSSIAN], they took us to Archangel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that-- you know, it becomes a little clearer the picture because then I was already-- I don't now, maybe three and a half, four, you now.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went to Archangel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- cars were provided, cattle cars were provided.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the people on the Russian border, Russia-Poland were evacuated to a safety area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Russian government.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after three or four weeks in those, we wound up on I think it must have been the White Sea because Archangel is on the White Sea.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I understand was that Russia and Poland at that time did not enjoy very friendly relations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Polish government was exiled to London, England at the onset of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
